{"tid":1143130,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"立山黑部行程一問","createTime":"2019-05-07T13:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T05:20:28.000Z","uid":101705,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f638fbc1daf7d84d887f956bf7ea22ddf95cc43","tid":1143130,"uid":101705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"Plan咗6月頭由大阪入名古屋走咁玩轉立山黑部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程：<br />\nDay 1: 中午機到大阪，9 fing，行吓激安咁就算<br />\nDay 2: 金澤，主要行兼六園，住金澤站附近<br />\nDay 3: 經白川鄉玩完去高山，住高山<br />\nDay 4: 行完朝市兜返去富山，去試吓so-called 最靚ge starfucks<br />\nDay 5:出發行立山黑部，住室堂<br />\nDay 6: 離開立山黑部坐JR 去松本，住松本<br />\nDay 7: 松本去名古屋，濕吓平咁<br />\nDay 8: 一朝早名古屋返香港<br />\n問題嚟啦，咁玩法我應該買北陸拱形pass+立山黑部加購券，之後果d直接買飛vs大阪果邊買飛+立山黑部、高山、松本pass vs 唔好煩一次過買晒2個pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋以上地方有咩好食好玩嘅地方可以推薦吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990023dbed51f0ab8591e4d3c79d6f2f979c4291","tid":1143130,"uid":27950,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"自己上乘換案內篤下計數機啦<br />\n咁都懶就買晒兩個PASS囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb347f9bb0364513b02932322e52e8c2881bf954","tid":1143130,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"洗鬼，北陸＋立山單程咪得"},{"pid":"6feba38aee26e22caef8144722666596ed66764a","tid":1143130,"uid":101705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb347f9bb0364513b02932322e52e8c2881bf954","tid":1143130,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"洗鬼，北陸＋立山單程咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"但計過由松本去名古屋jr 都成6000yen, 加埋立山加購又9800yen, 同我買個立山高山松本pass 差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b700347a12656be508ca6e147441df1d4679d44","ti